Game Info:
~~~~~~~~~~
Street Fighter III: Double Impact, the next title in one of the most prolific fighting game series is now on its way to the Dreamcast. Delivering two arcade hits in one CD, Street Fighter III: Double Impact contains Street Fighter III: New Generation and Street Fighter III: Second Impact. Street Fighter III: Double Impact sees the return of the series that started the fighting game phenomena more than a decade ago.